OL,3,C'We carry her magic every day': Couple
OL,4,Curge others to talk about baby loss
OL,6,FA couple whose daughter died shortly
OL,7,Fafter being born are urging more
OL,8,Fpeople to talk about what it is like
OL,9,Fto lose a baby.
OL,11,FSam and Sophie Brown from Lancashire
OL,12,Fgot to spend five days with their
OL,13,Fdaughter, Rosie, thanks to a special
OL,14,Fcold cot at Royal Preston Hospital.
OL,16,FThe 'Cuddle Cots' are cooling devices,
OL,17,Fallowing grieving families to have
OL,18,Fprecious extra time with their little
OL,19,Fones.
