OL,3,C'We carry her magic every day': Couple
OL,4,Curge others to talk about baby loss
OL,6,FIt has been almost four years since
OL,7,FRosie passed, and the family say she
OL,8,Fis with them in everything they do.
OL,10,FSophie said: "I left the world that I
OL,11,Fwas once in, and went into a different
OL,12,Fworld, that I never knew existed."
OL,14,FSophie, Sam, Lily and Rudy, their two
OL,15,Foldest children, spent time with
OL,16,FRosie, but moments like a walk in the
OL,17,Fpark were hard for the family.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
