OL,3,C'We carry her magic every day': Couple
OL,4,Curge others to talk about baby loss
OL,6,FSam said: "There's a photo of us
OL,7,Fwalking into the nature reserve...it
OL,8,Fwas meant to be the five of us walking
OL,9,Faround.
OL,11,F"But that moment is still a gift, and
OL,12,FI will never forget that."
OL,14,FThis is the first time Sophie and Sam
OL,15,Fhave felt ready to speak about her
OL,16,Fdeath, but to mark Baby Loss Awareness
OL,17,FWeek, they want people to know that
OL,18,Fit's ok to talk about baby loss.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
