OL,3,C'We carry her magic every day': Couple
OL,4,Curge others to talk about baby loss
OL,6,FSophie said: "You don't always know
OL,7,Fwhat to say, all you can do is ask how
OL,8,Fthey are, talk about them, ask how
OL,9,Fmuch they weighed.
OL,11,F"You're never going to remind someone
OL,12,Fthat they lost their baby.
OL,14,F"She's never going to come back, we
OL,15,Fcan't lose her again.
OL,17,F"But she's still with us and we have
OL,18,Fthe magic of Rosie, that we carry
OL,19,Fevery day."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
