OL,3,C'We carry her magic every day': Couple
OL,4,Curge others to talk about baby loss
OL,6,FSophie and Sam are still in contact
OL,7,Fwith their bereavement midwife from
OL,8,FRoyal Preston Hospital Claire
OL,9,FBraithwaite.
OL,11,FThe couple said in those early days,
OL,12,FClaire was like an angel they never
OL,13,Fknew they would need.
OL,15,FClaire helped them focus on making
OL,16,Fprecious memories with Rosie. Claire
OL,17,Ftold Granada Reports that the
OL,18,Fdifference in the couple now, compared
OL,19,Fto last year, is incredible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
