OL,3,C'We carry her magic every day': Couple
OL,4,Curge others to talk about baby loss
OL,6,FClaire said: "When sam and Sophie talk
OL,7,Fabout Rosie, you can see them just
OL,8,Fglow, their heart fills up with joy
OL,9,Fand they are so proud to be her
OL,10,Fparents.
OL,12,F"They are still grieving, they always
OL,13,Fwill be.
OL,15,F"You cannot upset grieving parents
OL,16,Fmore than they already are. If you
OL,17,Fignore the topic, or don't ask about
OL,18,Ftheir babies, that's more hurtful than
OL,19,Fnot talking about them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
