OL,3,C'We carry her magic every day': Couple
OL,4,Curge others to talk about baby loss
OL,6,FAfter losing Rosie, Sam threw himself
OL,7,Finto a gruelling fundraising challenge
OL,8,Fto help other families who've recently
OL,9,Flost a baby.
OL,11,FHe set himself the goal of rowing
OL,12,F6,480 metres every day for nine
OL,13,Fmonths. He and others raised over
OL,14,F#36,000 to fund 22 cuddle cots for
OL,15,Fhospitals without one.
OL,17,FSam said: "I thought what can we do to
OL,18,Fgive her her legacy...that's where
OL,19,FRowing for Rosie came from.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
